summary:
Add KitRae sword collection to Skyrim
By BOB666
descriptionHtml:
This mod is made by BOB666 !!!

You can craft these swords at any blacksmith forge. Stat base on Skyforge weapons. All Swords are 1handed so you can equip as dual wield :)
V2: Added Fatalis (Avoloch) Sword
